high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the tea pot that's to the right of the toaster.
Turn right and walk to the sink that's on your left then turn left to face it.
Clean the teapot off in the sink and then pick it back up and close the tap.
Walk back over to the stove and face the stove this time.
Put the teapot on the bottom right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean teapot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around to face the toaster.
Pick up the tea kettle from the counter.
Go to the sink on your right.
Go to the stove on your left.
Put the kettle on the front right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a kettle of water on the stove.

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go to the counter where the toaster is.
Pick up the teakettle from the counter.
Take the kettle to the sink on your left.
Fill the kettle with water at the sink.
Carry the kettle of water to the stove on your left.
Put the kettle on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a kettle of water on the stove.
